sequenceDiagram
    participant Kasir as Kasir (Lapis 1)
    participant Supir as Supir
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Fin as Finance (Lapis 2)

    Kasir->>API: 1. @click="onSubmit" (Draft Uang Saku Awal)
    Supir-->>Kasir: 2. Supir Pulang Bersama Kuitansi Fisik
    Kasir->>API: 3. Isi Realisasi (bbm, biayaEtoll)
    Kasir->>API: @click="onSubmit"
    Note right of API: Status = Pending Finance Validation
    Fin->>Fin: 4. Review Draft Uang Saku di /ledger
    Fin->>API: 5. @click="onPosting" (Finalize Validation)
    Note right of API: PULL_SALDO/PEMBELIAN di-append ke Buku Ledger Utama
